{"tid":1656154,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［召喚長跑撚］有運動商與警員教練終止合約","createTime":"2019-10-15T12:27:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T12:32:57.000Z","uid":299245,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"53fd1ce1731549d807180b35d82eebd8dd501d8e","tid":1656154,"uid":299245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:27:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191015/XYFDZ432QF5ZJBGVGKOMAM6WYE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191015%2FXYFDZ432QF5ZJBGVGKOMAM6WYE%2F&d=uOCBXhtcaqxtHROYLuBCLPzGhZJjjhZ%2BTSWVZI8Eykc%3D&h=25613b73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.sports.appledaily.com%2Fsports%2F20191015%2FXYFDZ432QF5ZJBGVGKOMAM6WYE%2F&h=6b5dde36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.sports.appledaily.com/sports/20191015/XYFDZ432QF5ZJBGVGKOMAM6WYE/</a><br />\n<br />\n早前有疑似警員在網上發表侮辱大學生言論，同為業餘跑手的他被披露受到運動品牌Asics贊助。有網民到Asics社交網站專頁留言，冀該品牌正視事件。Asics今日公佈，與疑為該名警員的易嘉麟已終止贊助協議。<br />\n日前在網上流傳一張社交網站截圖，消息指一位外號為「忌廉」的跑手指「啲中大生真係好吹得。個直播令人想笑。拘捕後被性暴？唔去驗傷？痴」疑為警員易嘉麟的帳號則留言「做天使做到shot（應該為short）左（咗）」，侮辱受害人。事後有網民指，易嘉麟為Asics贊助的跑手，有網民就到Asics社交平台專頁，要求該品牌交代。Asics今日指，易嘉麟已主動提出解除贊助協議，並已經生效。<br />\n據長跑界消息人士指，易嘉麟乃香港警隊中特別任務連成員，並沒有在前線參與處理示威的職務，但多次在網上發表侮辱示威者言論，引起多人不滿。據悉Asics一直考慮解決事件的方法，最後易嘉麟主動提出終止合作。<br />\n記者﹕禤家民<br />\n-------------------<br />\n<br />\n依加好多細跑會唔敢練習 怕被告非法集結<br />\n跑步撚係咪要支持一下A記？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nP牌仔第一次開post唔識開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2322c2377858e0c4318f3249cbb67042fdb1e275","tid":1656154,"uid":299245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:28:49.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"337e267f284fcc53e16625376e2655292673cc5c","tid":1656154,"uid":299245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:29:00.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"fb1518211aebb8aa77ad0bc92387719c0f90e943","tid":1656154,"uid":299245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:30:25.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"36df79448ac91296bba2adb65dc11cc75c1e0056","tid":1656154,"uid":299245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:31:48.000Z","msg":"4/10"},{"pid":"4402e64c2356c4162571d0c67962df6168b9e1a2","tid":1656154,"uid":299245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:32:03.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"c42eba9854a51cb0d326835d059c832814fcab75","tid":1656154,"uid":299245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:32:23.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"ca7e63099af8f3c96b224e2545e5c616b1b699e3","tid":1656154,"uid":299245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:32:33.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"624a9cc62feab3d2fc539402a66072534e6ab15d","tid":1656154,"uid":299245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:32:44.000Z","msg":"9/10"},{"pid":"9befc3ae6acb71c8d2881442e6960af90806c50f","tid":1656154,"uid":299245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T12:32:57.000Z","msg":"10/1」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}